title: Landmarks Berhad announces new COO for Treasure Bay Bintan
text:
Landmarks Berhad announces new COO for Treasure Bay Bintan   
Sep 21, 2015 Stefan Thumiger   
SINGAPORE - Landmarks Berhad today announced the appointment of a new Chief Operating Officer of Treasure Bay Bintan.
